body.name: MACHINIST X99 Dual CPU Motherboard, Intel (5th/6th Gen) LGA 2011-V3 Computer Server Motherboards (E-ATX, PCIe 3.0, DDR4, Dual LAN, Dual M.2, SATA 6Gb/s) for Intel Core i7, XEON E5 V3/V4 Series X99-D8
features: Intel dual CPU sockets: This c612 server chip motherboard is designed with dual CPU sockets, which improves performance by at least 50%, and can support Intel Core i7 5th/6th generation processors and Xeon E5 V3/V4 series processors. (Note: If only one CPU is installed, please install it in the right slot, and the graphics card needs to be installed in the bottom two slots.)

DDR4 4-channel memory slot: The memory slot of the LGA 2011-3 motherboard is designed with four channels, which can install 8 memory. It supports effective frequencies of 2133/2400/2666MHz(overclockable), and the maximum capacity is 256G.

If the amount of installed memory is less than 8, please fill the slots away from the CPU side first, that is, the "4" and "8" slots (just count from left to right). If you need to use four sticks of memory, please use slots "1", "4", "5", and "8" (counting from left to right).

PCIe 3.0 protocol standard: Equipped with 4 PCIe 3.0 X16 graphics card slots (with steel case). The transfer rate can reach 15.754 GB/s using one graphics card, and the performance can be improved by at least 50% by using two graphics cards. Equipped with dual M.2 hard disk slots, it can achieve fast reading even if multiple programs are running.

Stable power supply: use 24+8+8pin standard power supply interface (need to use a dedicated power supply for dual server motherboards), 12 (CPU) + 4 (memory) + 1 (X99 chip) phase power supply. Precise modularization provides good heat dissipation and makes the program run more stably.

Strong expandability: The X99 motherboard is equipped with multiple expansion interfaces to ensure that the motherboard has more room for improvement. These include 4*USB 3.0 ports, 4*USB 2.0 ports, 10*SATA 3.0 ports, 4*3pin sys fan, 2*4pin CPU fan. Besides, dual network ports allow your computer to do more things.

Tips: The package includes: 2*CPU fan bracket, 2*SATA cable, 1*I/O baffle, 1*motherboard. All the information of this product can be found in the description and pictures. If you don't know where to download the driver, it is recommended to use the Win 10 system, which can help you solve all driver problems.

Note: If you need the motherboard to enter the BIOS, please press the "Del" key continuously after pressing the startup key. Please do not wait until the startup LOGO screen appears on the computer screen before operating, because it is already too late.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great cheap X99 board that supports lga 2011v3 cpu's
reviews.reviewText: Worked perfect right out of the box did a test boot outside the pc case and it just booted right up used a E5 2680V3 cpu and it works great with this motherboard very happy with this purchase Windows install recognized my 1Tb nvme right away and it boots very quick to Windows

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars It crashes all the time.
reviews.reviewText: The board came packaged perfectly. Easy to set up. I am running my i7-6900k, 32 gig ddr4 ram, DEEPCOOL GAMMAXX GT A-RGB cpu, rx 480 8 gig gpu, i have a nvme installed. It will not find it. That is the first flaw. The bios has way too many options. And I am running my Samsung Evo 870 1 TB 2.5" SSD as my main drive. 650w PSU. LG 4k monitor. N3XT case.This mother board crashes all the time. I heard it word. I thought it wouldn't. I have to now find a different bios. That is the only fix. It feels sluggish, slow, my ram is not running to the full potential. But the crashing is the biggest issue. I am not even running a heavy demanding game. Unreal Tournament 2004 is my go to right now. 200 FPS. But right in the middle of the game it will crash, and it is violent. It sends a loud ear splitting screech through your head phones when it crashes. And you have to manually restart your computer every time. BUT IT CAN JUST BE SITTING ON THE DESKTOP AS WELL AND IT WILL JUST FREEZE.Once I am caught up on bills I am going to get a different board. This one is JUNK.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2021
reviews.reviewText: I bench tested this machine against the motherboard on my son’s machine from Best-Buy and it stomped it with better speed. With this motherboard my son says he turns the settings and resolutions all the way up on the online games now. Some of that is of course the video card etc..This board works well for me in that it was easy to setup and run with no issues. I liked its price and used it as a test board. My other motherboard died in a very strange way (LED showed no motherboard issues and no video out...but video-card was good) I really needed a "known good" to troubleshoot..One downside of this purchase was that the documentation was still being created. I needed the exact pins for Power/reset switches on front panel. The company was fantastic about getting me the images and text needed in a timely manner. They were great!.The second downside (for me) was that it only has four ram slots. I have tons of memory but in quantity of sticks so would have to use it elsewhere. If you're new to building PC's this might be a great ticket for creating a game machine..Given all the hacking from Russia and China, I hope someone verifies the board doesn’t call any mothership when its on your network. Just saying we live in those times.

reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars The pins that seat the CPU, 4 are both bent or missing
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. It seems like a decent motherboard but I can't tell if the pins won't let the CPU compute. I have a 2695 v4 and this motherboard is for a 2011-3 socket. Might have to try out a different motherboard board. Everything else seems to be ok though. I'm buying a different model because I'm having troubles sending it back. Can't get to a UPS store. But I'm gonna see if it's just that motherboard. Don't want to give the company a bad review for one faulty motherboard. We'll see on motherboard number 2.

The vrm is 3 phase not four and should be check to make sure heat sink is mounted properly to vrm as well I'd stay to lower core count CPUs I found the vrm is a issue with larger CPUs as in no advantage of having 10 core or 14 core when hashing away so the vrm is definitely hindering the larger chips iv tested it with a few. CPUs and it. Lives with a 2680v4 in it now the max ram of 32gb was a surprise and not a welcome one but all in all I use this board for a ton of applications and games and it's never let us down 1070 2070 no bottlenecks

reviews.reviewTitle: Buena opción para budget gaming xeon, el BIOS es horrible pero se puede modificar
reviews.reviewText: La compre para una pc gamer budget x99 xeon. La manufactura es de calidad pero el bios original es una basura, pero se puede modificar usando el software MI889 de miyconst; le pude agregar soporte para ReBAR y la capacidad de modificar los timings de la RAM para dejarla en XMP.Para gaming queda perfecta con un xeon e5-2667 que esta actualmente en solo 1000 pesitos, de las pocas X99 de este tamaño con quad channel para la RAM DDR4.Actualmente la uso con una rtx 3090, 64gb RAM y puedo correr juegos AAA en 4K en ultra con ray tracing sostenido arriba de 70fps.Ya solo estoy siguiendo un i7-6950X (es el mejor CPU que soporta) para en cuanto esté en un precio decente hacerle el upgrade.

reviews.reviewTitle: Do yourself a favor, don't buy this!
reviews.reviewText: I had to return the first mobo because the 1st pciex slot did not work and the Realtek sound controller did not get detected. Got another one, and it was worst! Not only did the first pciex slot still did not work either, but none of the nvme m.2 card got detected at all by the bios, meaning it could not boot from my perfectly fine m.2 nvme ssd...Really dissappointed with this product... I do NOT recommend this brand at all!

Es war schon sehr verwunderlich das ich statt einen roten, einen grünen Karton erhalten hatte. Fazit Katon falsch Mainboard richtig. In dem Karton lag nur das Mainboard sonst nichts, keine Beschreibung keine Software nichts. Auch im Netz keinerlei Support, keine Software zum Download null. Ich habe das Board zum laufen bekommen und es läuft gut, aber ein Leie sollte die Finger davon lassen.
Demorou 84 anos pra chegar, se soubesse tinha comprado no Brazil, paguei taxa pra alfandega e o vendedor me reembolso logo após.
